    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，方向设为BT。那标题我写成\"Continuous development (bottom-to-top)\"可以吗？另外流程上是不是先有一个初始commit，然后从main切出develop分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
