      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，标题没问题。流程上：main先有一个初始commit，然后checkout到develop做第一次开发提交，接着回到main把develop合并进来。这是第一轮迭代。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout develop",
        "commit",
        "checkout main",
        "merge develop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第一轮画好了。develop分支还在，我让它继续存在进行第二轮开发？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "commit",
        "merge develop"
